Cue Card Topic: Describe Your Favorite Teacher

Introduction
My favorite teacher is Mr. Sharma. He taught me English when I was in school. He is one of the most inspiring teachers in my life.

Appearance and Personality
He is tall and always wears simple and neat clothes. He has a calm voice and a friendly smile. He is very kind and patient with students.

Why I Like Him
I like him because he explains difficult topics in a very simple way. He always encourages students to ask questions. He also motivated me to improve my English speaking skills.

What I Learned From Him
From him, I learned confidence, discipline, and the importance of education. He taught us not only subjects but also good manners and life values.

Conclusion
I feel very lucky to have such a great teacher in my life. He has played an important role in my success.
